        the magic :meth:`__array__` method) to convert Sage matrices
        to numpy arrays::

            sage: # needs numpy
            sage: import numpy
            sage: b = numpy.array(a); b
            array([[ 0,  1,  2,  3],
                   [ 4,  5,  6,  7],
